            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span style="color: #c44a08;">+</span> Installation on interior walls with no existing chimney</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span style="color: #c44a08;">+</span> Basement and below-grade installation</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span style="color: #c44a08;">+</span> Zero indoor air quality impact from combustion</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span style="color: #c44a08;">+</span> No conditioned indoor air drawn into the combustion chamber</li>
